{"tid":2208483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台美破獲中共駭客組織 FBI：台灣是可信任夥伴","createTime":"2020-09-19T03:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T03:12:09.000Z","uid":7736,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fff575c3f0fb8b54ddfa09e47b4e8a55e001be","tid":2208483,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"新唐人亞太台 2020 年 09 月 18 日訊】美國司法部16日宣布起訴五名中共駭客，台灣也有企業受害。台灣調查局表示，五月份調查台灣能源公司被駭客攻擊案，發現駭客的雲端主機設在美國加州，調查局隨即提供相關資料給美方，台美合作破案。調查局長說，希望作為合作打擊跨境犯罪的典範。美方FBI駐台代表表示，面對跨國網路犯罪，需要與可信任的夥伴合作，台灣是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20200918/video/279106.html?fbclid=IwAR07bPt7zz8ZKjSQH1IadZdtf3jp0bcDsFglCP1aa0_dlvNp-TX5ySG6YLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fb5%2F20200918%2Fvideo%2F279106.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR07bPt7zz8ZKjSQH1IadZdtf3jp0bcDsFglCP1aa0_dlvNp-TX5ySG6YLw&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=2ba9ba38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20200918/video/279106.html?fbclid=IwAR07bPt7zz8ZKjSQH1IadZdtf3jp0bcDsFglCP1aa0_dlvNp-TX5ySG6YLw</a><br />\n<br />\n原來之前單嘢，係台灣幫手發現"},{"pid":"a657ae523dcee02bcbbcd40e8613a83b0d1db7a1","tid":2208483,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"taiwan no. 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c82dc825a2efcecaff56c0f71c002de3ab05d47","tid":2208483,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"想搞鳩唐鳳地頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d20ca3cf08939db840ebd989167675fa480ad5","tid":2208483,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:12:09.000Z","msg":"唐鳳本身就係hacker<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}